(97, 1, '2013-01-25 10:22:35', '2013-01-24 23:22:35', '&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;img src="http://archmagento.com/leyven/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/slider-pics1.jpg" alt="slider-pics" width="960" height="290" /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h4&gt;Bookkeeping service for Sydney Hills District businesses&lt;/h4&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nLeyven Bookkeeping Pty Ltd is a CPA Business located in the beautiful\nHills District of northwest Sydney and was established by its principal,\nEvelyn (Eve) Durham to provide bookkeeping excellence to small\nbusinesses.\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nAll general bookkeeping tasks including reviewing your current bus-\niness bookkeeping methods, training &amp;amp; workers compensation.\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nBAS (Business Activity Statement) advice, preparation &amp;amp; lodgement\nand dealing with commissioner on your behalf.\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nManagement of GST including transaction coding. We will make\nsure all GST reports are submitted accurately and on time.\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nBookkeeping training and MYOB training to help improve the per-\nformance of both you and your staff.\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n\nWe offer a small business consulting service to help you understand\nfinancial reports, develop systems and solve problems.\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\nCall us today on &lt;strong&gt;0414 899 487&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="#"&gt;&lt;img alt="leave-message" src="http://archmagento.com/leyven/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/leave-message.png" width="162" height="38" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;BAS&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;GST&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;MYOB&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h3&gt;PAYG&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;Overview of the bookkeeping services we can provide.&lt;/h2&gt;\nAre you looking for a bookkeeper with extensive small business accounting\nexperience?\n\n&lt;strong&gt;Small Business Owners&lt;/strong&gt; - When it comes to making important business\ndecisions, access to accurate and up to date information about your business\nis crucial. Leyven Bookkeeping can help you make this happen.\n\n&lt;strong&gt;Professional Accountants&lt;/strong&gt; - Experience counts. Leyven Bookkeeping knows\nwhat you expect from a bookkeeping service. We can provide your valued\nclients with general bookkeeping or a specialised reviewer bookkeeping\nservice. Call Eve on &lt;strong&gt;0414 899 487&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="#"&gt;More...&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;About our main bookkeeper - Eve Durham.&lt;/h2&gt;\nEve is a CPA with a Bachelor of Economics (major in Accounting). Prior to\ncreating her own business, Eve gained more than 20 years experience in a\nchartered firm environment, including 6 years with KPMG. Eve is required to\nupdate her professional knowledge regularly and to maintain a high level of\nquality control in her business. &lt;a href="#"&gt;More...&lt;/a&gt;\n\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '96-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-25 10:22:35', '2013-01-24 23:22:35', '', 96, 'http://leyven.com.au/?p=97', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(98, 1, '2015-06-06 22:32:45', '2015-06-06 12:32:45', '<div class="content-wrapper">\n<div class="page-content">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col s12 m6 offset-m3 l6 card leftCardHome">\n<div class="left-title">\n<h4>Bookkeeping service for Sydney Hills District businesses</h4>\n</div>\n<div class="left">\n<div class="left-content">\n\n<p class="topText">Leyven Bookkeeping Pty Ltd is a CPA Business located in the beautiful Hills District of northwest Sydney and was established by its principal, Evelyn (Eve) Durham to provide bookkeeping excellence to small businesses.</p>\n<div class="box card">\n\nAll general bookkeeping tasks including reviewing your current business bookkeeping methods, training &amp; workers compensation.\n\n</div>\n<div class="box card">\n\nBAS (Business Activity Statement) advice, preparation &amp; lodgement<br />\nand dealing with the ATO on your behalf.\n\n</div>\n<div class="box card">\n\nManagement of GST including transaction coding. We will make<br />\nsure all GST reports are accurate and submitted on time.\n\n</div>\n<div class="box card">\n\nBookkeeping training and MYOB training to help improve the performance of both you and your staff.\n\n</div>\n<div class="box card">\n\nWe offer a small business consulting service to help you understand<br />\nfinancial reports, develop systems and solve problems.\n\n</div>\n<p class="contact">Call us today on <strong>0414 899 487</strong> or <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn" href="<code><?php  ?>/contact/"><i class="mdi-communication-quick-contacts-mail left"></i>Leave a Message</a><p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="col s12 m6 offset-m3 l6 card rightCardHome blue-grey darken-1">\n<div class="row center">\n<div class="col s12 m3 l3 card-panel center services">\n<h3>BAS</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="col s12 m3 l3 card-panel center services">\n<h3>GST</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="col s12 m3 l3 card-panel center services">\n<h3>MYOB</h3>\n</div>\n<div class="col s12 m3 l3 card-panel center services">\n<h3>PAYG</h3>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class="right-content">\n<h2 class="center">Overview of the bookkeeping services we can provide</h2>\nAre you looking for a bookkeeper with extensive small business accounting experience?\n\n<strong>Small Business Owners</strong> - When it comes to making important business decisions, access to accurate and up to date information about your business is crucial. Leyven Bookkeeping can help you make this happen.\n\n<strong>Professional Accountants</strong> - Experience counts. Leyven Bookkeeping knows what you expect from a bookkeeping service. We can provide your valued clients with general bookkeeping or a specialised reviewer bookkeeping service. Call Eve on <strong>0414 899 487</strong> <a href="/bookkeeping/">More...</a>\n<h2 class="center">About our principle bookkeeper - Eve Durham</h2>\nEve is a CPA with a Bachelor of Economics (major in Accounting). Prior to creating her own business, Eve gained more than 20 years experience in chartered firm environments, including 6 years with KPMG. Eve is required to update her professional knowledge regularly and to maintain a high level of quality control in her business. <a href="/about-us/">More...</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '96-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-06-06 22:32:45', '2015-06-06 12:32:45', '', 96, 'http://leyven.com.au/?p=98', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
