(166, 1, '2013-01-26 11:13:58', '2013-01-26 00:13:58', '<span style="color: #333333;">Leyven Bookkeeping Pty Ltd is a CPA Business located in the beautiful Hills District of northwest Sydney.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #333333;">Leyven Bookkeeping was established by its principal, Evelyn (Eve) Durham to provide bookkeeping excellence to small businesses.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #333333;">Eve is a CPA with a Bachelor of Economics (major in Accounting). Prior to creating her own business, Eve gained more than 20 years experience in a chartered firm environment, including 6 years with KPMG. In her small business roles with these firms, Eve enjoyed helping small business owners to achieve their goals. Eve has worked with clients in a variety of businesses including legal firms, cafes, Chartered Accountants, medical consultants, real estate, tourism, plumbing services, film production and share investment and now also include catering, occupational therapy, specialist dental services, fashion retailing, motorcycle repair and maintenance.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #333333;">As a CPA, Eve is required to update her professional knowledge regularly and to maintain a high level of quality control in her business.</span>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-26 11:13:58', '2013-01-26 00:13:58', '', 2, 'http://leyven.com.au/2-revision-16/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
