(204, 1, '2013-01-30 13:45:19', '2013-01-30 02:45:19', '<div class="sub-page-content">\r\n	<div class="sub-page-content-left">\r\n		<div class="sub-page-info">\r\n			<h2>Bookkeeping</h2>\r\n			<p><span><strong>Leyven Bookkeeping offer a professional, reliable & flexible onsite or off site service to suit your needs</strong></span></p>\r\n			<p>We can arrange a weekly, fortnightly, monthly or quarterly bookkeeping service to fit in with your business schedule and ATO lodgement requirements. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>All work is performed by a qualified CPA with more than 20 years of accounting experience in assisting small business.Our on-site service covers the North-West area of Sydney including the suburbs of Baulkham Hills, Beecroft, Bella Vista, Berowra, Blacktown, Castle Hill, Carlingford, Cherrybrook, Dural, Glenhaven, Glenorie, Glenwood, Eastwood, Epping, Hornsby, Kellyville, Kellyville Ridge, Kenthurst, Kurrajong, North Rocks, Pennant Hills, Quakers Hill, Seven Hills, Stanhope Gardens, Thornleigh, Richmond, West Pennant Hills, Westleigh and Windsor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If your business is located outside these areas please \r\ncontact Eve to enquire about our off-site service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We love what we do and can ensure you are up to \r\ndate and your financial records are organised! </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our services include  : <br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Data Entry</li>\r\n<li>Inventory</li>\r\n<li>Setup accounting software</li>\r\n<li>Profit and Loss Statement</li>\r\n<li>Reconciliation and reporting of Accounts Receivable/Payable</li>\r\n<li>Bank, credit card and loan reconciliations</li>\r\n<li>Payroll setup and processing including superannuation reports</li>\r\n<li>BAS & IAS preparation and lodgement</li>\r\n<li>Setup of Chart of Accounts including GST coding</li>\r\n<li>Balance Sheet </li>\r\n<li>Cash Flow Reports</li>\r\n<li>Budgets</li>\r\n<li>Management Reports</li>\r\n<li>Recommend record keeping improvements</li>\r\n<li>Preparation of records for Accountant</li></ul></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We currently provide bookkeeping services using the following accounting software :<br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>MYOB</li>\r\n<li>Xero</li>\r\n<li>QuickBooks</li></ul></p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Bookkeeping', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '104-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-30 13:45:19', '2013-01-30 02:45:19', '', 104, 'http://leyven.com.au/104-revision-8/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(205, 1, '2013-01-30 13:21:46', '2013-01-30 02:21:46', '				<div class="sub-page-content">\r\n					<div class="sub-page-content-left">\r\n						<div class="sub-page-info">\r\n							<h2>About Us</h2>\r\n							<p>123Leyven Bookkeeping Pty Ltd is a CPA Business located in the beautiful Hills District of northwest Sydney.</p>\r\n							<p>Leyven Bookkeeping was established by its principal, Evelyn (Eve) Durham to provide bookkeeping excellence to small businesses.</p>\r\n							<p>Eve is a CPA with a Bachelor of Economics (major in Accounting). Prior to creating her own business, Eve gained more than 20 years experience in a chartered firm environment, including 6 years with KPMG. In her small business roles with these firms, Eve enjoyed helping small business owners to achieve their goals. Eve has worked with clients in a variety of businesses including legal firms, cafes, Chartered Accountants, medical consultants, real estate, tourism, plumbing services, film production and share investment and now also include catering, occupational therapy, specialist dental services, fashion retailing, motorcycle repair and maintenance.</p>\r\n							<p>As a CPA, Eve is required to update her professional knowledge regularly and to maintain a high level of quality control in her business.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n		', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-01-30 13:21:46', '2013-01-30 02:21:46', '', 2, 'http://leyven.com.au/2-revision-19/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
