(287, 1, '2013-02-05 10:10:01', '2013-02-04 23:10:01', '<div class="sub-page-content">\r\n<div class="sub-page-content-left">\r\n<div class="sub-page-info">\r\n<h2>Bookkeeping</h2>\r\n<span><strong>Leyven Bookkeeping offer a professional, reliable &amp; flexible on-site or off-site service to suit your needs</strong></span>\r\n\r\nWe can arrange a weekly, fortnightly, monthly or quarterly bookkeeping service to fit in with your business schedule and ATO lodgement requirements.\r\n\r\nAll work is performed by a qualified CPA with more than 20 years of accounting experience in assisting small business. Our on-site service covers the North-West area of Sydney including the suburbs of Baulkham Hills, Beecroft, Bella Vista, Berowra, Blacktown, Castle Hill, Carlingford, Cherrybrook, Dural, Glenhaven, Glenorie, Glenwood, Eastwood, Epping, Hornsby, Kellyville, Kellyville Ridge, Kenthurst, Kurrajong, North Rocks, Pennant Hills, Quakers Hill, Seven Hills, Stanhope Gardens, Thornleigh, Richmond, West Pennant Hills, Westleigh and Windsor.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignright size-full wp-image-234" alt="record" src="http://leyven.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/record.jpg" width="357" height="238" data-id="234" />If your business is located outside these areas please contact Eve to enquire about our off-site service.\r\n\r\nWe love what we do and can ensure that you are \r\nup to date and your financial records are organised!\r\n\r\nOur services include :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Data Entry</li>\r\n	<li>Inoicing</li>\r\n	<li>Setup accounting software</li>\r\n	<li>Profit and Loss Statement</li>\r\n	<li>Bank, credit card and loan reconciliations</li>\r\n	<li>BAS &amp; IAS preparation and lodgement</li>\r\n	<li>Budgets</li>\r\n	<li>Inventory</li>\r\n	<li>Balance Sheet</li>\r\n	<li>Cash Flow Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Setup of Chart of Accounts including GST coding</li>\r\n	<li>Reconciliation and reporting of Accounts Receivable/Payable</li>\r\n	<li>Payroll setup and processing including superannuation reports</li>\r\n	<li>Share Investment record keeping</li>\r\n	<li>Management Reports</li>\r\n	<li>Recommend record keeping improvements</li>\r\n	<li>Preparation of records for Accountant</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe currently provide bookkeeping services using the following accounting software :\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>MYOB</li>\r\n	<li>Xero</li>\r\n	<li>QuickBooks</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Bookkeeping', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '104-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-02-05 10:10:01', '2013-02-04 23:10:01', '', 104, 'http://leyven.com.au/104-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
