(299, 1, '2013-02-06 18:19:21', '2013-02-06 07:19:21', '<div class="content-wrapper">\r\n<div class="page-content">\r\n<div class="page-left">\r\n<div class="left-title">\r\n<h4>Bookkeeping service for Sydney Hills District businesses</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="left">\r\n<div class="left-content">\r\n\r\nLeyven Bookkeeping Pty Ltd is a CPA Business located in the beautiful Hills District of northwest Sydney and was established by its principal, Evelyn (Eve) Durham to provide bookkeeping excellence to small businesses.\r\n<div class="box">\r\n\r\nAll general bookkeeping tasks including reviewing your current bus- <br />\r\niness bookkeeping methods, training &amp; workers compensation.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n\r\nBAS (Business Activity Statement) advice, preparation &amp; lodgement<br />\r\nand dealing with the ATO on your behalf.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n\r\nManagement of GST including transaction coding. We will make<br />\r\nsure all GST reports are accurate and submitted on time.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n\r\nBookkeeping training and MYOB training to help improve the per-<br />\r\nformance of both you and your staff.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="box">\r\n\r\nWe offer a small business consulting service to help you understand<br />\r\nfinancial reports, develop systems and solve problems.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nCall us today on <strong>0414 899 487</strong> <a href="/contact/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-100 message" title="leave-message" alt="" src="http://leyven.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/leave-message.png" width="162" height="38" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="page-right">\r\n<div class="buttons">\r\n<div class="bottons">\r\n<h3>BAS</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bottons">\r\n<h3>GST</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bottons">\r\n<h3>MYOB</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="bottons">\r\n<h3>PAYG</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="right-content">\r\n<h2>Overview of the bookkeeping services we can provide.</h2>\r\nAre you looking for a bookkeeper with extensive small business accounting experience?\r\n\r\n<strong>Small Business Owners</strong> - When it comes to making important business decisions, access to accurate and up to date information about your business is crucial. Leyven Bookkeeping can help you make this happen.\r\n\r\n<strong>Professional Accountants</strong> - Experience counts. Leyven Bookkeeping knows what you expect from a bookkeeping service. We can provide your valued clients with general bookkeeping or a specialised reviewer bookkeeping service. Call Eve on <strong>0414 899 487</strong> <a href="/bookkeeping/">More...</a>\r\n<h2>About our principle bookkeeper - Eve Durham.</h2>\r\nEve is a CPA with a Bachelor of Economics (major in Accounting). Prior to creating her own business, Eve gained more than 20 years experience in \r\nchartered firm environments, including 6 years with KPMG. Eve is required to update her professional knowledge regularly and to maintain a high level of quality control in her business. <a href="/about-us/">More...</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '96-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-02-06 18:19:21', '2013-02-06 07:19:21', '', 96, 'http://leyven.com.au/96-revision-15/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
